title: 'Meh'
body: Don't expect the box to be much useful. It is very flimsy and the pieces separating the sections are detachable and get loose all the time. The screw driver is total s#!t as you can see in the pics. But haven't found any problem with the screws so far. Might be a bit over priced though.

title: 'Has most screws for most laptops'
body: Happy with the purchase but screw's collection is limited!
